<Algorithm code="         1. Let _C_ be ? Get(_O_, *&#34;constructor&#34;*).         1. If _C_ is *undefined*, return _defaultConstructor_.         1. If _C_ is not an Object, throw a *TypeError* exception.         1. Let _S_ be ? Get(_C_, %Symbol.species%).         1. If _S_ is either *undefined* or *null*, return _defaultConstructor_.         1. If IsConstructor(_S_) is *true*, return _S_.         1. Throw a *TypeError* exception.       ">
